From: Thomas Gleixner <tglx@linutronix.de>
Date: Sat, 25 Jul 2009 16:17:02 +0200
Subject: video: Convert vga console lock to raw_spinlock

We want to printk from atomic contexts even on rt. Make the console
lock raw.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Gleixner <tglx@linutronix.de>

---
 drivers/video/console/vgacon.c |   42 ++++++++++++++++++++---------------------
 1 file changed, 21 insertions(+), 21 deletions(-)

Index: linux-2.6-tip/drivers/video/console/vgacon.c
===================================================================
